    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "so when people use that term, is it actually about things being factually wrong, or is it just a way for politicians to call things \"fake\" when they don't like the reporting? like, does it work both ways or is it mostly just a tactic used by certain groups?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
